sql: SELECT d_year, s_nation, p_category , SUM(lo_revenue) - SUM(lo_supplycost) AS profit FROM ssb.p_lineorder LEFT JOIN ssb.dates ON lo_orderdate = d_datekey LEFT JOIN ssb.customer ON lo_custkey = c_custkey LEFT JOIN ssb.supplier ON lo_suppkey = s_suppkey LEFT JOIN part ON lo_partkey = p_partkey WHERE c_region = 'AMERICA' AND s_region = 'AMERICA' AND (d_year = 1997 OR d_year = 1998) AND (p_mfgr = 'MFGR#1' OR p_mfgr = 'MFGR#2') GROUP BY d_year, s_nation, p_category ORDER BY d_year, s_nation, p_category
